Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:05.98,HiguDef,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I see you've gotten in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:10.14,HiguDef,,0,0,0,,{\be1}We aren't holding back just because it's a festival!
